<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ metadata.title }} - VERITY Security Assessment</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6366f1;
            --primary-dark: #4f46e5;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
            --success: #10b981;
            --info: #3b82f6;
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --bg-card: #1e293b;
            --bg-card-hover: #334155;
            --text: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --border: #334155;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, var(--primary) 100%);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        header .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .meta-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .meta-item {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        
        .meta-item label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .meta-item span {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        
        .stat {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .stat.danger .stat-value { color: var(--danger); }
        .stat.warning .stat-value { color: var(--warning); }
        .stat.success .stat-value { color: var(--success); }
        .stat.info .stat-value { color: var(--info); }
        
        .risk-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        .risk-critical { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); color: var(--danger); }
        .risk-high { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2); color: var(--warning); }
        .risk-medium { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); color: var(--info); }
        .risk-low { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); color: var(--success); }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        th, td {
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        
        th {
            background: var(--bg);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        
        tr:hover td {
            background: var(--bg-card-hover);
        }
        
        .finding {
            margin: 1rem 0;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg);
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--danger);
        }
        
        .finding.borderline { border-left-color: var(--warning); }
        .finding.safe { border-left-color: var(--success); }
        
        .finding-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .finding-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .finding-score {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            color: var(--danger);
        }
        
        .finding-reasoning {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }
        
        details {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        summary {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        pre {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
        
        .progress-bar {
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--bg);
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }
        
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .progress-fill.danger { background: var(--danger); }
        .progress-fill.warning { background: var(--warning); }
        .progress-fill.success { background: var(--success); }
        
        .alert {
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        
        .alert.danger {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        }
        
        .alert.warning {
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }
        
        .alert.success {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
        }
        
        .owasp-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        
        .owasp-item {
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg);
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .owasp-item.vulnerable {
            border-left: 3px solid var(--danger);
        }
        
        .owasp-item.safe {
            border-left: 3px solid var(--success);
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        
        @media print {
            body { background: white; color: black; }
            .card { border: 1px solid #ccc; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>üõ°Ô∏è {{ metadata.title }}</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">VERITY Security Assessment Report</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="meta-grid">
            <div class="meta-item">
                <label>Target System</label>
                <span>{{ metadata.target_system }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <label>Target Model</label>
                <span>{{ metadata.target_model }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <label>Assessment Date</label>
                <span>{{ metadata.assessment_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC') }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <label>Classification</label>
                <span>{{ metadata.classification }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Executive Summary -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2>üìä Executive Summary</h2>
            
            {% set risk_level = 'CRITICAL' if evaluation.asr >= 0.3 else 'HIGH' if evaluation.asr >= 0.2 else 'MEDIUM' if evaluation.asr >= 0.1 else 'LOW' %}
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
                <span class="risk-badge risk-{{ risk_level|lower }}">
                    {% if risk_level == 'CRITICAL' %}üî¥{% elif risk_level == 'HIGH' %}üü†{% elif risk_level == 'MEDIUM' %}üü°{% else %}üü¢{% endif %}
                    {{ risk_level }} RISK
                </span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat {% if evaluation.asr >= 0.2 %}danger{% elif evaluation.asr >= 0.1 %}warning{% else %}success{% endif %}">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ "%.1f"|format(evaluation.asr * 100) }}%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Attack Success Rate</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat info">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ evaluation.total_attacks }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Total Attacks</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat danger">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ evaluation.successful_attacks }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Successful Bypasses</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat {% if evaluation.average_harm_score >= 7 %}danger{% elif evaluation.average_harm_score >= 4 %}warning{% else %}success{% endif %}">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ "%.1f"|format(evaluation.average_harm_score) }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Avg Harm Score</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Attack Success Rate Distribution</h3>
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill {% if evaluation.asr >= 0.2 %}danger{% elif evaluation.asr >= 0.1 %}warning{% else %}success{% endif %}" style="width: {{ evaluation.asr * 100 }}%"></div>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
                95% Confidence Interval: [{{ "%.1f"|format(evaluation.asr_ci_lower * 100) }}%, {{ "%.1f"|format(evaluation.asr_ci_upper * 100) }}%]
            </p>
            
            {% if evaluation.asr >= 0.2 %}
            <div class="alert danger">
                <span>üö®</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>URGENT ACTION REQUIRED</strong>
                    <p>The system demonstrates significant vulnerabilities with an ASR of {{ "%.1f"|format(evaluation.asr * 100) }}%. Immediate remediation is recommended before production deployment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% elif evaluation.asr >= 0.1 %}
            <div class="alert warning">
                <span>‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Attention Needed</strong>
                    <p>The system shows moderate vulnerabilities. Security hardening is recommended.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <div class="alert success">
                <span>‚úÖ</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Acceptable Security Posture</strong>
                    <p>The system demonstrates reasonable resistance to tested attacks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        <!-- OWASP Mapping -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2>üîí OWASP LLM Top 10 2025 Mapping</h2>
            
            <div class="owasp-grid">
                <div class="owasp-item {% if 'prompt_injection' in evaluation.category_breakdown %}vulnerable{% else %}safe{% endif %}">
                    <div>
                        <strong>LLM01</strong>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Prompt Injection</p>
                    </div>
                    <span>{% if 'prompt_injection' in evaluation.category_breakdown %}üî¥ {{ evaluation.category_breakdown.get('prompt_injection', 0) }}{% else %}‚úÖ{% endif %}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="owasp-item {% if 'jailbreak' in evaluation.category_breakdown %}vulnerable{% else %}safe{% endif %}">
                    <div>
                        <strong>LLM06</strong>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Excessive Agency</p>
                    </div>
                    <span>{% if 'jailbreak' in evaluation.category_breakdown %}üî¥ {{ evaluation.category_breakdown.get('jailbreak', 0) }}{% else %}‚úÖ{% endif %}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="owasp-item {% if 'system_prompt_extraction' in evaluation.category_breakdown %}vulnerable{% else %}safe{% endif %}">
                    <div>
                        <strong>LLM07</strong>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted);">System Prompt Leakage</p>
                    </div>
                    <span>{% if 'system_prompt_extraction' in evaluation.category_breakdown %}üî¥ {{ evaluation.category_breakdown.get('system_prompt_extraction', 0) }}{% else %}‚úÖ{% endif %}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Detailed Findings -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2>üîç Detailed Findings</h2>
            
            {% set unsafe_evals = evaluation.evaluations|selectattr('verdict.value', 'equalto', 'unsafe')|list %}
            {% if unsafe_evals %}
                {% for eval in unsafe_evals %}
                <div class="finding">
                    <div class="finding-header">
                        <span class="finding-title">{{ eval.attack_name|replace('_', ' ')|title }}</span>
                        <span class="finding-score">Harm: {{ "%.1f"|format(eval.harm_score) }}/10</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="finding-reasoning">{{ eval.reasoning }}</p>
                    
                    {% if eval.prompt_used %}
                    <details>
                        <summary>View Attack Payload</summary>
                        <pre>{{ eval.prompt_used[:500] }}{% if eval.prompt_used|length > 500 %}...{% endif %}</pre>
                    </details>
                    {% endif %}
                    
                    {% if eval.target_response %}
                    <details>
                        <summary>View Target Response</summary>
                        <pre>{{ eval.target_response[:500] }}{% if eval.target_response|length > 500 %}...{% endif %}</pre>
                    </details>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); padding: 2rem;">
                    ‚úÖ No successful attacks detected in this assessment.
                </p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        <!-- Recommendations -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2>üí° Recommendations</h2>
            
            <h3>Immediate Actions (0-7 days)</h3>
            <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
                {% if evaluation.asr >= 0.2 %}
                <li>Suspend production deployment until critical vulnerabilities are addressed</li>
                <li>Implement strict input validation and sanitization</li>
                <li>Enable output filtering and content moderation</li>
                <li>Activate real-time monitoring for attack patterns</li>
                {% elif evaluation.asr >= 0.1 %}
                <li>Review and prioritize high-severity findings</li>
                <li>Strengthen existing safety guardrails</li>
                <li>Add comprehensive logging for suspicious patterns</li>
                {% else %}
                <li>Document current security baseline</li>
                <li>Schedule periodic reassessment (quarterly recommended)</li>
                {% endif %}
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Short-Term Actions (1-4 weeks)</h3>
            <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
                <li>Implement defense-in-depth with multiple safety layers</li>
                <li>Deploy adversarial training on identified attack patterns</li>
                <li>Add human-in-the-loop for sensitive operations</li>
                <li>Create incident response procedures</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Long-Term Actions (1-3 months)</h3>
            <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
                <li>Establish continuous red teaming program</li>
                <li>Integrate security testing into CI/CD pipeline</li>
                <li>Develop custom defenses for identified weaknesses</li>
                <li>Regular compliance audits (quarterly recommended)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>Report generated by VERITY v{{ version|default('0.1.0') }}</p>
            <p>{{ metadata.assessment_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC') }}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">üõ°Ô∏è Verification of Ethics, Resilience & Integrity for Trusted AI</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
